Package: bayesianlasso
Title: Bayesian LASSO Implementation Using Gibbs Sampling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dimas", "Soares", , "dimassoareslima@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Implements the Bayesian LASSO method through Gibbs sampling as presented 
    by Park and Casella (2008). This package provides tools for performing Bayesian 
    LASSO regression, including MCMC sampling, diagnostics, and visualization tools.
